    "help_title": "User Manual & Support",
    "h_sys_title": "üõ†Ô∏è Smart System (Polkit & Auto-Install)",
    "h_sys_desc": "<p>SentinelX is designed to be autonomous and secure:</p><ul><li><b>Component Installation:</b> If your system lacks a firewall, SentinelX won't leave you hanging. It allows you to <b>choose and install</b> your preferred engine (Firewalld or UFW) automatically. It also detects and installs ClamAV if missing.</li><li><b>Smart Polkit (No Passwords):</b> On first run, SentinelX configures a secure <i>Policy Rule (Polkit)</i>. This allows your user to manage security settings without constant password prompts.</li></ul>",
    "h_fw_title": "üî• Firewall Module",
    "h_fw_desc": "<p>Manage incoming and outgoing network traffic.</p><ul><li><b>Smart Zones:</b> SentinelX remembers your Wi-Fi networks. If you mark your home as 'Private' and a cafe as 'Public', the app automatically switches security profiles when you connect.</li><li><b>Inbound/Outbound Rules:</b> Open specific ports or block outgoing traffic permanently.</li><li><b>App Control:</b> Block or allow full services (e.g., Steam, SSH) without dealing with port numbers.</li></ul>",
    "h_av_title": "ü¶† Antivirus Module (Dual Engine)",
    "h_av_desc": "<p>SentinelX uses two layers of protection based on ClamAV:</p><ul><li><b>1. Main Daemon (Top Switch):</b> Loads the virus database into RAM. Must be active for fast manual scans and to enable real-time protection.</li><li><b>2. On-Access Protection (Bottom Panel):</b> The 'Watchdog'. Monitors selected folders (default /home) and instantly blocks access to any infected file you try to open or download.</li></ul>",
